sub_title: Co-founder & CEO of IOMETE | Helping the world become smarter with our fully-managed modern data stack.
summary:
Building the Data Infrastructure-as-a-Platform for start/scale-ups!

Building and maintaining data infrastructure is complex, and engineers are scarce and expensive. Start/Scale-ups should be focused on growth, not distractions like building data infrastructure.

The Solution
Instead of building and maintaining your own data stack, use our platform.
iomete is the first complete data infrastructure delivered as a single platform. It’s an all-in-one solution that replaces Snowflake (Lakehouse), Databricks (Jobs and ETL), Fivetran (onboarding 3rd party data), Informatica (Data Governance), and Looker/Tableau (BI) with a single platform.

Benefits
- Free up your engineers; no integrations, no maintenance
- Leverage experts that understand your needs and that have built infrastructure for organizations in all growth stages, including Uber and Google
- Fully managed, no maintenance, no headaches
- Easy-to-use, become data-driven in a heartbeat
- Scales with you
- Save $$$
Our platform is used by customers ranging from a Series A fintech startup to a multi-billion oil corporation. Leverage experts that understand your needs and that have built infrastructure for organizations in all growth stages, including Uber and Google.
